# Competitor Monitoring Agent (Power Automate)

This project demonstrates an automated competitor monitoring workflow built using Microsoft Power Automate.

The agent automatically collects updates from RSS feeds and sends summarized updates through email.

## Workflow Overview

1. Recurrence trigger runs the automation on a schedule.
2. The flow reads configuration data from an Excel table.
3. RSS feeds are collected for monitoring.
4. Each RSS item is evaluated using conditions.
5. Relevant updates are stored in a variable.
6. A summarized report is sent via email.

## Key Components

Recurrence  
Initialize Variable  
Excel Table Data Retrieval  
RSS Feed Monitoring  
Conditional Filtering  
Email Notification

## Use Case

Businesses often monitor competitors manually.  
This automation reduces manual effort by automatically collecting and delivering relevant competitor updates.

